  "body": "Hello guys üëã \r\n\r\nFirst, thank you for you work on this awesome Ethereum client! \r\nAppologize for not using discord for asking a questions but the invitation had expired üëê \r\n\r\nI saw this PR #2908 removing `snapshot.mode` flag. The flag I've used to quicker sync the mainnet node previously. \r\nHowever this PR #3117 and also [erigon-snapshot repo](https://github.com/ledgerwatch/erigon-snapshot) make me optimistic that the feature won't be removed.\r\n\r\nSo my questions are:\r\n- how can I speed up syncing by using snapshots in the recent version?\r\n- can you elaborate more about the plans regarding this feature?\r\n\r\nThanks for the reply!\r\n\r\n\r\n",
